            <div>
               
	<pb facs="liv_002016_0001" n="0001"/>
<opener>
<lb/><add rend="gray" hand="#U1">5-6-9</add> <add place="above marginright" rend="gray" hand="#U1">ms 8/11</add> <dateline rend="right"><placeName><geogName type="island">Zanzibar</geogName></placeName> <date when="1864-04-25">25 April
<lb/>1864</date></dateline>
<lb/>    
<lb/><salute>My Dear Sunley,</salute>
</opener>

<lb/><p rend="center">We left <placeName><country><choice><orig><w>Mosam-<lb break="no"/>-bique</w></orig><reg><w>Mozam-
<lb break="no"/>-bique</w></reg></choice></country></placeName> on <date when="1864-04-16">16<hi rend="sup underline">th</hi></date> and 
<lb/>arrived here on the
<lb/><date when="1864-04-23">23<hi rend="sup underline">rd</hi></date> hoping to meet
<lb/>you, <subst><del><gap extent="1" unit="words" agent="overwriting"/></del><add place="over-text"><gap extent="1" unit="words" agent="illegible"/></add></subst> have
<lb/>been unfortunate
<lb/>enough to miss 
<lb/>you - We set out
<lb/>with the intention
<lb/>of calling at <placeName><geogName type="island">Johanna</geogName></placeName> -
<lb/>- paying the odd <orgName><placeName><geogName type="island">Johanna</geogName></placeName> man</orgName> and

	<pb facs="liv_002016_0002" n="0002"/>
<lb/><add place="above marginleft" rend="gray" hand="#U1">2</add> and then push on to
<lb/>this place to which
<lb/>we heard you had
<lb/>come - but we made
<lb/>more leeway than
<lb/>we expected, and
<lb/>either that, or the
<lb/>current swept us,
<lb/>on the second day,
<lb/>past the latitude of
<lb/><placeName><geogName type="island">Johanna</geogName></placeName>, and to
<lb/>about <measure>70 miles</measure>
<lb/>west of the south
<lb/>end of <placeName><geogName type="island">Great Comoro</geogName></placeName>-
<lb/>We tried to sail to
<lb/>the east but in

	<pb facs="liv_002016_0003" n="0003"/>
<lb/><measure>six hours</measure> only <add place="above marginright" rend="gray" hand="#U1">3</add>
<lb/>made <measure>eight <add place="below">^</add> <add place="above">miles</add></measure> of
<lb/>Easting - Then
<lb/>made away for <placeName><geogName type="island">Zanzibar</geogName></placeName> - I knew
<lb/>that you were very 
<lb/>anxious to see
<lb/><persName>Rae</persName>, and I was
<lb/>very desirous to
<lb/>confer with you
<lb/>about the future
<lb/>but we have
<lb/>very unluckily
<lb/>been deprived
<lb/>of the pleasure -</p>

	<pb facs="liv_002016_0004" n="0004"/>
<lb/><p><add place="above marginleft" rend="gray" hand="#U1">4</add> I was bringing
<lb/>a waggon capable
<lb/>of carrying your 
<lb/>heavy machinery
<lb/>and now place it
<lb/>in <persName>M<hi rend="sup underline">s</hi> De Witte</persName>'s
<lb/>charge for you -
<lb/>I have a small
<lb/>box of medicines
<lb/>from the <placeName><region>Ariel</region></placeName>
<lb/>for you and some
<lb/>seeds from the
<lb/><placeName><region>Cape</region></placeName> which I put
<lb/>into the same charge </p>
<lb/><p><term type="occupation">Captain</term><persName>Frazer</persName>

	<pb facs="liv_002016_0005" n="0005"/>
<lb/>took the <add place="margintop" rend="gray" hand="#U1">5</add> waggon <add place="above marginright" rend="gray" hand="#U1">MS 8/11</add> instead
<lb/>of <persName>de Witte</persName> and I
<lb/>see he has it mounted
<lb/>I have to hurry away
<lb/>as fast as possible
<lb/>on account of
<lb/>the nearness of the
<lb/>breaking up of the
<lb/><seg type="weather">Monsoon</seg>. -</p>
<lb/><p>I send through
<lb/><persName>D<hi rend="sup underline">r</hi> Seward</persName> the
<lb/>sum of Â£18 for 
<lb/>the <placeName><geogName type="island">Johanna</geogName></placeName> man
<lb/>left unpaid -
<lb/>It is rather more

	<pb facs="liv_002016_0006" n="0006"/>
<lb/><add place="above marginleft" rend="gray" hand="#U1">6</add> than his due as
<lb/>he had advances
<lb/>but he may
<lb/>have it.</p>
<lb/><p>The loss of <persName>Rae</persName>
<lb/>is a disadvantage
<lb/>to me but I hope
<lb/>he will be all
<lb/>you wish - &amp; that
<lb/>your undertaking
<lb/>will prosper - </p>

<closer>
<lb/><salute>Ever yours</salute><!-- Change as appropriate -->
<lb/><signed><persName>David Livingstone</persName></signed><!-- Change as appropriate --> 
</closer>

